@startuml
!theme plain
hide footbox
autonumber

actor "APP" as APP
participant "Middleware" as MW
participant "Banco de Comercio" as BDC

title POST /bdc/accounts/get-cvu-accounts?token=<JWT_APP>
APP -> MW: POST /bdc/accounts/get-cvu-accounts
MW -> MW: Validar JWT APP
MW -> MW: Calcular X-SIGNATURE
MW -> BDC: POST /accounts/get-cvu-accounts
note right of MW
Headers: Authorization + X-SIGNATURE
end note
BDC --> MW: listado subcuentas / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 4xx / 5xx

@enduml
